{"tid":2246023,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"無法滿足需求，傳 NVIDIA 將自三星轉單台積電","createTime":"2020-10-16T16:48:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-16T18:32:25.000Z","uid":56533,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"07dc28261ef7f2e8b4b1dfab397789c63f256768","tid":2246023,"uid":56533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T16:48:18.000Z","msg":"近期晶圓代工龍頭台積電先進製程滿載，無法大規模承接其他訂單的情況下，使競爭對手南韓三星陸續拿下繪圖晶片大廠輝達（NVIDIA）及行動處理器龍頭高通的大單。不過外媒《Guru3D》報導，因三星無法快速又大規模生產 NVIDIA Ampere 架構 GPU，因此 NVIDIA 目前決定轉單台積電。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，目前 NVIDIA Ampere 架構的遊戲顯卡全部由南韓三星生產，但面對產能不足、市場供不應求的問題，NVIDIA 開始規劃將大部分業務轉單台積電。之前，已有國內媒體指出，NVIDIA 已預訂台積電在 2021 年 7 奈米製程的大量產能。<br />\n<br />\n消息指出，NVIDIA 轉移訂單的原因，除了台積電 7 奈米產品良率相對穩定，另一個原因是之前計劃分散風險，以因應三星 8 奈米製程良率問題。之前市場就有傳出，三星為拉近與台積電的晶圓代工市場市占距離，就不惜以較台積電更低報價搶單。再加上台積電 2020 下半年之後，先進製程早已處於滿載狀態，無法對增加的訂單提供產能，因此許多客戶轉單給南韓三星。<br />\n<br />\n報導進一步表示，雖然目前還不確定台積電會從 2021 年的什麼時候開始生產 NVIDIA 轉來的晶片生產訂單，以及是哪種產品會採用台積電製程，不過因台積電即將在 15 日舉行 2020 年第 3 季的線上法人說明會，預料也將成為法人積極關注的焦點。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://cdn.technews.tw/2020/10/14/nvidia-transfer-order/?utm_source=fb_finance&amp;utm_medium=facebook&amp;fbclid=IwAR1Da5K3momsS74QK6S4g9s7QpNEILEllXC_7IclOqwu6IO2GUPNyOZAJ3c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.technews.tw%2F2020%2F10%2F14%2Fnvidia-transfer-order%2F%3Futm_source%3Dfb_finance%26utm_medium%3Dfacebook%26fbclid%3DIwAR1Da5K3momsS74QK6S4g9s7QpNEILEllXC_7IclOqwu6IO2GUPNyOZAJ3c&d=6FpmejEDNbHOA1ae24hao72U0TaxigNo3Nw2L1ZdNcs%3D&h=449a8b4c\" target=\"_blank\">https://cdn.technews.tw/2020/10/14/nvidia-transfer-order/?utm_source=fb_finance&amp;utm_medium=facebook&amp;fbclid=IwAR1Da5K3momsS74QK6S4g9s7QpNEILEllXC_7IclOqwu6IO2GUPNyOZAJ3c</a>"},{"pid":"c5c9212a44c5647cc8e5425a8f6f255291423ed1","tid":2246023,"uid":67500,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T17:34:42.000Z","msg":"三星咁屎"},{"pid":"e320cbcbcef3c804c0e607e44d97992560abb93f","tid":2246023,"uid":64701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T17:47:48.000Z","msg":"傳 NVIDIA RTX 3000 下年用返 7nm TSMC<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2242441\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2242441</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3e632e89da70325c6e873d8123d2fc7d7687a7fd","tid":2246023,"uid":66365,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T18:03:41.000Z","msg":"第一水高價搶個班情何以堪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"667fd3e11a9020510996e7582f628d02221c459b","tid":2246023,"uid":239558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3e632e89da70325c6e873d8123d2fc7d7687a7fd","tid":2246023,"uid":66365,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T18:03:41.000Z","msg":"第一水高價搶個班情何以堪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T18:15:19.000Z","msg":"睇唔到 我唔知 我唔信 我無睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8732df468dadb027ce7a77d904e806874c70b101","tid":2246023,"uid":144,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T18:32:25.000Z","msg":"$3080收漏電版rtx3080<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}